<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="SimpleMauiApp._8section">
    <ScrollView>
        <VerticalStackLayout>
            <!-- Chapter Title -->
            <Label 
                Text="The Future of Operating Systems"
                FontSize="24"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                HorizontalOptions="Center"
                Margin="10" />

            <!-- Introduction -->
            <Label 
                Text="As technology advances, Operating Systems must adapt to meet new demands. This chapter explores emerging trends and challenges shaping the future of OS design."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" />

            <!-- AI-Driven Operating Systems -->
            <Label 
                Text="1. AI-Driven Operating Systems"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="Artificial Intelligence (AI) is set to revolutionize OS functionality. Future systems may leverage AI for predictive resource allocation, intelligent process management, and enhanced security."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: AI-driven performance optimization in modern smartphones."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Quantum Computing -->
            <Label 
                Text="2. Operating Systems for Quantum Computers"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="Quantum computing introduces a paradigm shift in processing power. OSs designed for quantum computers will need to manage qubits, quantum algorithms, and hybrid classical-quantum tasks."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Experimental systems like Qiskit Runtime."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Edge Computing and IoT -->
            <Label 
                Text="3. Edge Computing and IoT"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="With the rise of IoT devices and edge computing, OSs will need to support decentralized processing, low-latency communication, and real-time analytics."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Lightweight OSs like TinyOS for IoT devices."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Cybersecurity Challenges -->
            <Label 
                Text="4. Enhanced Cybersecurity"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="As cyber threats evolve, future OSs must integrate robust security measures, such as AI-driven intrusion detection, end-to-end encryption, and zero-trust architectures."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Integration of security-focused designs like SELinux."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Green Computing -->
            <Label 
                Text="5. Green Computing and Energy Efficiency"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="Energy-efficient OSs are critical for sustainability. Future systems may focus on reducing power consumption through intelligent resource management and energy-aware scheduling."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Power-saving features in modern mobile OSs."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Cloud and Virtualization -->
            <Label 
                Text="6. Cloud-First and Virtualized Environments"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="Cloud-native and virtualized OSs will dominate, offering seamless scalability, cross-platform compatibility, and containerized application support."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Kubernetes for container orchestration."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- User-Centric Designs -->
            <Label 
                Text="7. User-Centric Operating Systems"
                FontSize="18"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                Margin="10" />
            <Label 
                Text="Future OSs will prioritize personalized experiences, offering adaptive interfaces, voice and gesture control, and enhanced accessibility for diverse user groups."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />
            <Label 
                Text="Example: Adaptive interfaces in modern mobile OSs like Android and iOS."
                FontSize="14"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Start" />

            <!-- Closing Thoughts -->
            <Label 
                Text="The future of Operating Systems lies in innovation, adaptability, and addressing global challenges. As technology evolves, OSs will continue to be at the heart of progress, empowering individuals and industries worldwide."
                FontSize="16"
                Margin="10"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" />

            <!-- Final Button -->
            <Button
                Text="Test"
                BackgroundColor="Blue"
                TextColor="White"
                FontAttributes="Bold"
                HorizontalOptions="Center"
                VerticalOptions="End"
                Margin="10"
                Clicked="NextClicked"/>
        </VerticalStackLayout>
    </ScrollView>
</ContentPage>